    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Black Pine: Incident Response </strong>is a multiplayer horror survival game set in the aftermath of intense solar flares that have wreaked havoc across the Appalachian Mountains. Your team has been dispatched to restore critical infrastructure that supports the local region. But as you take on perilous repairs—fixing power grids, unstable radar towers, and vital water systems—strange and unknown forces begin to emerge, with sightings of lurking horrors in the shadows. Dark secrets haunt these mountains, turning every task into a potential nightmare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every mission demands tight teamwork, quick thinking, and constant communication as you tackle high-stakes, dangerous repairs in a hostile environment. Each task teeters on the edge of disaster, turning routine fixes into desperate struggles for survival. In <strong>Black Pines</strong>, survival is about more than just restoring what’s broken—it’s about facing the shadows together and hoping to make it out alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/3c0787ae8f5fcbf3fb293c6965159768.avif?t=1732585119\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras_big/3c0787ae8f5fcbf3fb293c6965159768.avif?t=1732585119 width=800 height=177 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every contract challenges your crew to work together, combining skills and strategies to tackle high-stakes repairs and get the job done. Split up to cover more ground or stick together for maximum efficiency—it’s all about teamwork. Share tools, communicate effectively, and stay focused on your goals to complete contracts faster and earn more cash. Prove your worth, rake in the rewards, and build your reputation as the best damn crew the Appalachians have ever seen!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/605a566b8fd431151431ea2cc14975ca.poster.avif?t=1732585119\" width=750 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/605a566b8fd431151431ea2cc14975ca.webm?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/605a566b8fd431151431ea2cc14975ca.mp4?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/d4206207bde0869dd31803b396493285.poster.avif?t=1732585119\" width=800 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/d4206207bde0869dd31803b396493285.webm?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Brave the rugged Appalachian wilderness to restore critical systems—power grids, water pumps, radar towers, and more! Stay alert as you hunt for hidden resources and clues that might explain the strange outages and eerie incidents plaguing the region. But it’s not just about fixing what’s broken—you’ll need to outsmart the lurking dangers and survive the hostile environment. Every repair edges you closer to uncovering something massive… and deeply unsettling.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/cce6525e811354976b9a6cb3e59d1555.poster.avif?t=1732585119\" width=750 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/cce6525e811354976b9a6cb3e59d1555.webm?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/cce6525e811354976b9a6cb3e59d1555.mp4?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/12c28217b93f4bf242a5ba4a30349c7e.poster.avif?t=1732585119\" width=750 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/12c28217b93f4bf242a5ba4a30349c7e.webm?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/12c28217b93f4bf242a5ba4a30349c7e.mp4?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/90f3f1d05d74ddf95b26bbae99447ab2.poster.avif?t=1732585119\" width=800 height=177 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/90f3f1d05d74ddf95b26bbae99447ab2.webm?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Having the right tool isn’t just helpful—it’s essential. Each contract presents unique challenges, from fixing complex power grids to repairing water systems or radar towers. Whether it’s a heavy-duty wrench, a diagnostic device, or your chainsaw that is heavy, loud, and built for destruction! Using the right equipment can mean the difference between success and failure. Choose wisely, share tools with your team, and upgrade your gear to take on tougher missions. The better your tools, the faster you’ll work—and the more cash you’ll make.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/8b7e0563da4998ac5e8982954c112afc.poster.avif?t=1732585119\" width=750 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/8b7e0563da4998ac5e8982954c112afc.webm?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/8b7e0563da4998ac5e8982954c112afc.mp4?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/929e3741dac93e49cdce6c913b7ee0ce.poster.avif?t=1732585119\" width=750 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/929e3741dac93e49cdce6c913b7ee0ce.webm?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/929e3741dac93e49cdce6c913b7ee0ce.mp4?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/c3a957734f6a9481dbd65d851b2417c5.poster.avif?t=1732585119\" width=750 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/c3a957734f6a9481dbd65d851b2417c5.webm?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/c3a957734f6a9481dbd65d851b2417c5.mp4?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/dba333585bf64089d2a0b7d95e8d6d97.poster.avif?t=1732585119\" width=750 height=312 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/dba333585bf64089d2a0b7d95e8d6d97.webm?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3266110/extras/dba333585bf64089d2a0b7d95e8d6d97.mp4?t=1732585119\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
